Package: instanceengineering
Type: Package
Title: High-Performance Binary Over/Under Sampling
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Joao", "B. G. de Brito", email = "joaosabby@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides high-performance binary over- and under-sampling routines
    using ADASYN and NearMiss-1. The implementation uses numeric matrices,
    optional native C kernels, Rfast fallbacks, and configurable nearest-neighbor
    backends for exact or approximate searches.
